flickcurl
------------------------------------------
Flickcurl is a C library for the Flickr API, handling creating the requests,
signing, token management, calling the API, marshalling request parameters and
decoding responses. It uses libcurl to call the REST web service and libxml2 to
manipulate the XML responses. Flickcurl supports all of the API (see Flickcurl
API coverage for details) including the functions for photo/video uploading,
browsing, searching, adding and editing comments, groups, notes, photosets,
categories, activity, blogs, favorites, places, tags, machine tags,
institutions, pandas and photo/video metadata. It also includes a program
flickrdf to turn photo metadata, tags, machine tags and places into an RDF
triples description.

Runtime requirements:
  bash-4.4.12-3
  cygwin-3.2.0-1
  libcurl4-7.78.0-1
  libflickcurl-devel-1.26-1bl1
  libflickcurl0-1.26-1bl1
  libraptor2-devel-2.0.15-1
  libraptor2_0-2.0.15-1
  libxml2-2.9.10-2
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.37-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  libcurl-devel-7.78.0-1
  libraptor2-devel-2.0.15-1
  libtool-2.4.6-7
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://librdf.org/flickcurl/

Canonical download:
  https://download.dajobe.org/flickcurl/flickcurl-1.26.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack flickcurl-1.26-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./flickcurl-1.26-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/flickcurl-1.26-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/flickcurl-1.26-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libflickcurl0-1.26-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libflickcurl-devel-1.26-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(flickcurl)
  /usr/bin/flickcurl.exe
  /usr/bin/flickrdf.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/flickcurl.README
  /usr/share/doc/flickcurl/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/flickcurl/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/flickcurl/COPYING.LIB
  /usr/share/doc/flickcurl/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/flickcurl/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/flickcurl/NOTICE
  /usr/share/doc/flickcurl/README
  /usr/share/man/man1/flickcurl.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/flickrdf.1.gz

(libflickcurl0)
  /usr/bin/cygflickcurl-0.dll

(libflickcurl-devel)
  /usr/bin/flickcurl-config
  /usr/include/flickcurl.h
  /usr/lib/libflickcurl.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/flickcurl.pc
  /usr/share/man/man1/flickcurl-config.1.gz

